In the INTEREST OF M.C., Minor Child, D.Z., Mother, Appellant, N.C., Father, Appellant. No. 18-1131 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 5, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

A mother and father appeal the termination of their parental rights to their minor child. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
